001
002package com.commercetools.importapi.client;
003
004import java.util.UUID;
005
006import io.vrap.rmf.base.client.http.CorrelationIdProvider;
007
008public class ImportCorrelationIdProvider implements CorrelationIdProvider {
009    private final String projectKey;
010
011    public ImportCorrelationIdProvider(String projectKey) {
012        this.projectKey = projectKey;
013    }
014
015    @Override
016    public String getCorrelationId() {
017        return projectKey + "/" + UUID.randomUUID();
018    }
019}
